{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "奈迪犹（Fes限定Ver.） 第1话 精灵战争",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "本角色剧情涉及\\n主线剧情第23章后篇的\\n核心内容。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "嘎噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（唔……没法一击毙命！\\n难道是受到了泽诺斯复活的影响吗，\\n魔兽都变强了……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "哥哥！这样太危险了！\\n你这样只身一人一直消耗下去的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（塞西娅……为了之后的战斗，\\n我们需要保存巴哈姆特的力量。\\n所以现在就由我自己来……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……\\n解决掉了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕噜……嘎啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔！？竟然还没死！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "巴哈姆特！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹！抱歉让你出手救我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "虽说对手已经没有力气了，但你能\\n轻松一击就消灭魔兽……看来你已经\\n对巴哈姆特的力量运用自如了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "（力量在不断涌出……\\n巴哈姆特的力量似乎\\n已经逐渐适应我的身体了。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "（很好。\\n继续适应下去，\\n我就能够获得更加强大的力量……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "（唔！？怎么回事？\\n巴哈姆特的力量……\\n正在逐渐被封印……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120245_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "（呃！这种感觉……我有印象。\\n这是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹，你没事吧！？\\n我看你突然间解除了龙化……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "是精灵秘术吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01",
                "110367_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "原来如此……也就是说一旦龙化\\n就会发动精灵秘术，\\n巴哈姆特之力也会随之被封印吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "没错。\\n精灵国曾为了研究巴哈姆特之力\\n而在我身上施加了很多秘术。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "刚刚龙化解除的前一刻\\n我有与那时相同的感觉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "到底是谁给你施了这种秘术呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我心里大概有数……\\n为了确认这点，\\n我需要回一趟精灵国。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "确实巴哈姆特之力\\n在今后的战斗中不可或缺……\\n好吧，那我们暂时分头行动吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们会边清理沿路的魔兽\\n边向勒福克斯进发。\\n我们就在勒福克斯会合！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "好的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "（精灵国吗。\\n好久都没来过这市区了，\\n不过……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "森林被毁坏了大半啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "城墙上再多布置些弓兵！\\n木盾上也要涂上泥以防火攻！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芩。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "奈迪犹？你怎么来了……\\n你不是去格拉姆斯了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "出了点问题需要回来一趟。\\n不过……这到底怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "森林里有战斗的痕迹，\\n市区里也到处都是士兵和战斗人偶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "看到那些的话你应该已经明白了吧？\\n现在战争一触即发。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "究竟是哪个国家在进攻这里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "不是国家，而是前国王——\\n我那愚蠢的父王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "你离开这里后，\\n他和评议会的那些家伙合谋\\n逼迫我退位。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芬罗达他……\\n可事到如今他为何又……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "似乎是因为我破坏了圣树。\\n说是……\\n侵犯圣域之人不配为精灵王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n然后你拒绝了退位要求，\\n所以现在精灵国内即将爆发一场内战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "没错。\\n我可不会屈服于父王。\\n无论他如何施压，我都不会让他如愿的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "说说你吧，奈迪犹。\\n你又是怎么回事？\\n不是说出了什么问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "嗯。我有事想问你。\\n事情是这样的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "嚯，封印龙化的秘术吗。\\n嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "“临化”秘术的话，\\n确实能够为龙化设下限制。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "我不记得自己给你施过这种秘术，\\n所以应该是芬罗达吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "他曾经用你的身体研究过巴哈姆特。\\n也许是当时用来确保安全的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但之前我也曾龙化过不止一次，\\n为什么到现在才发动？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "巴哈姆特的力量很强大。\\n所以可能是花了一些时间\\n才适应了你的身体吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "秘术一旦发动就无法轻易解除。\\n原本让芬罗达来为你解除\\n是最好的选择……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "但现在很不巧，\\n我和他正处于对立的局面。\\n想见他应该不容易。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芬罗达那家伙……真会给人找事。\\n看来不先解决精灵国的内乱，\\n我的问题也解决不了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "平息内乱？\\n你竟然肯为精灵国做事，\\n这可真是稀奇。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "把那家伙揪出来是最快的方法。\\n为了打倒“起始之人”，\\n我没有时间浪费了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "呵呵……也是。\\n那我们就再并肩作战一次吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120222_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达的部下",
            "context": "报告！\\n芬罗达军开始行动了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "来了吗……很好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "在正门前部署战斗人偶部队，\\n各个主干道两侧也都派兵埋伏。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120222_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达的部下",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "那家伙行动得比我想象中还快，\\n看来是非常希望我下台啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这完全不像是那个优柔寡断\\n一直隐居的家伙的风格啊。\\n也许他另有企图。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "不，你错了，奈迪犹。\\n他可不是优柔寡断，\\n只是擅长出尔反尔而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100039_03_00_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "那家伙除了自身利益，不考虑\\n其他任何事情。所以才会\\n出尔反尔地做出这种动摇国家的行为。",
